text: Flag of Tokelau Tokelau competed at the 2015 Pacific Games in Port Moresby, Papua New Guinea from 4 to 18 July 2015. The country was represented by one athlete, one coach and two officials. Tokelau was one of two countries that did not win a medal during the games. ==Squash== {| |- | 40px || |} ;Men * Sam Ben Sipili Iasona ==References== Pacific Games Category:Nations at the 2015 Pacific Games Category:Tokelau at the Pacific Games
